See pod for documentation, in lib/Mojolicious/Plugin/BasicAuth.pm

Installation

cpan Mojolicious::Plugin::BasicAuth

Get source:
git clone git://github.com/tempire/mojolicious-plugin-basicauthcondition.git

Basic Usage

	# Mojolicious::Lite
	plugin 'basic_auth'

	get '/' => sub {
	    my $self = shift;
	    return unless $self->helper( basic_auth => realm => username => 'password' );
	    ...
	}

(See Mojolicious::Plugin::BasicAuth POD for more)

